            <lg xml:id="TK842">
<l>aṟivilā ṉeñcuvan tītal piṟituyātu</l>
<l>millai peṟuvāṉ ṟavam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The cause of) a fool cheerfully giving (something) is nothing else but the receiver's merit (in a former birth).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
